rows.label: qst200302_msg0001
rows.name:
The rockfall is at Zalmor's
Crevice, near the Genbu Drifts.

rows.label: qst200302_msg0002
rows.name:
Please! Save my friends! We
can't do anything by ourselves!

rows.label: qst200302_msg0101
rows.name:
To think the rockfall was
the work of a Gogol...

rows.label: qst200302_msg0102
rows.name:
But just a little while ago,
a Gogol came here to Teos
Aure and went on a rampage.

rows.label: qst200302_msg0103
rows.name: I don't know where it went.

rows.label: qst200302_msg0104
rows.name:
How about you try asking
the townspeople?

rows.label: qst200302_msg0201
rows.name: It seems the Gogol fled the city.

rows.label: qst200302_msg0202
rows.name:
If you follow its footprints, you
might be able to track it down.

rows.label: qst200302_msg0203
rows.name:
Causing rockfalls, attacking
the city... We can't let a
dangerous monster run loose.

rows.label: qst200302_msg0204
rows.name:
Please, defeat it and
bring peace back to us!
